H0.text: Who was the first NASA astronaut to conduct a spacewalk. Neil Armstrong

H1.text: Who was the first NASA astronaut to conduct a spacewalk. Buzz Aldrin

H2.text: Who was the first NASA astronaut to conduct a spacewalk. John Glenn

H3.text: Who was the first NASA astronaut to conduct a spacewalk. Ed White

A4.text: On June 3, 1965, White became the first American to walk in space.

A5.text: the highlight of the mission was the first space walk by an American, during which White floated free outside the spacecraft

A6.text: The first American spacewalk was performed on June 3, 1965, by Ed White from the second crewed Gemini flight, Gemini IV, for 21 minutes.
